data.description: Impeccably maintained, this three-bedroom, three-bathroom home has been thoughtfully updated inside and out. The unfinished basement presents limitless opportunities for personalized touches. Outside, the landscaped backyard boasts a charming patio and mature trees, perfect for entertaining guests. Nearby Sulphur Gulch & Tallman Gulch trails invite exploration of the area's natural beauty. Additionally, residing within an HOA grants access to an outdoor water park with pools tailored for both adults and children. Situated just minutes away from Black Bear Golf Course and Downtown Parker, residents enjoy convenient access to cultural amenities like The Parker Arts, Culture & Events Center, local library, shops, restaurants, and the Main Street Farmer's Market. Don't miss this chance to make this property your own!
